data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome in the tranquil community of Dixie Pine Meadows! This adorable home offers an open layout that seamlessly combines the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or enjoying quiet evenings in.  Generously sized bedrooms offer plenty of natural light, creating a peaceful and serene atmosphere Relax and unwind in the tranquility of your own private oasis in the backyard.  Beyond the walls, this townhome is nestled in a quiet community and with nearby amenities such as parks, shopping centers, and restaurants, everything you need is just a short distance away.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this townhome yours. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!  All information herein is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed. Buyer is responsible to verify all listing information, including square feet/acreage, to buyer's own satisfaction. The listing broker's offer of compensation is made only to participants of the MLS where the listing is filed.
